description: Scandinavian Enviro Systems AB engages in the development and sale of processes and products relating to the recycling of plastics and tires from vehicles in the environmental sector. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 23 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2014-06-18. The company has a patented technology for recovering carbon black, oil, steel and gas from waste tyres. The firm conducts sales of key facilities, receives royalties related to technology from installations sold by the Company, sales of servicing and training for established facilities, as well as operates a plant through wholly-owned subsidiary Tyre Recycling in Sweden AB. The plant serves as a large-scale production test and demo plant and includes all the process steps and solutions featured in a full-scale plant. The Company’s main shareholder is Pegroco Venture AB.
name: Scandinavian Enviro Systems AB
